      "content": "it's not just about stepping away though. i tried that. i stayed home, i blocked people, i literally tried to disappear and they still find ways to make me feel like i'm the problem. it feels like no matter what i do, the world just keeps pushing. it's like i'm trapped in this loop of misery and there's just no way out. it's like the only way to actually stop the noise is to just... not be here anymore. it feels more like a solution than a tragedy at this point.",
